Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:25.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}{\3c&HE3BD66&}切なく雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:30.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}まだ何も君を知らないよ
